86
00:04:05.700 --> 00:04:07.330
Jangan bersikap konyol.

87
00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:09.839
Minta maaflah dan pikirkan cara agar kalian bisa akur.

88
00:04:09.869 --> 00:04:11.869
